    <description>
        <p>
            Blockbench is a free, modern model editor for low-poly and boxy
            models with pixel art textures. Models can be exported into
            standardized formats, to be shared, rendered, 3D-printed, or used
            in game engines. There are also multiple dedicated formats for
            Minecraft Java and Bedrock Edition with format-specific features.
        </p>
        <p>
            Blockbench features a modern and intuitive UI, plugin support and
            innovative features. It is the industry standard for creating
            custom 3D models for the Minecraft Marketplace.
        </p>
    </description>
